icreate_controller:
  A ROS python package for easy control of the actions of the iRobot Create roomba robot

Installation:
  Just use the command git pull "git://github.com/CurryBoy/icreate_controller.git" in a directory that is accessible to ROS
  To add a directory to ROS add "ROS_PACKAGE_PATH=path_to_your_directory:$ROS_PACKAGE_PATH" to your .bashrc file
  
Use:
  All the information on how to use to the package is found at https://github.com/CurryBoy/icreate_controller/wiki

License:
